{"tid":1393224,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員根本唔係政治中立，政治中立 = 服從政府？","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:50:13.000Z","uid":274055,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"026e92ad59a34a8e4ca6c5da241c6027c4971646","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"政府有政治取態（支持修例、不作調查等），<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>支持政府就係支持一種政治取態</ins></span>，點算係政治中立？公務員根本唔係政治中立，中立唔係要不偏幫嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果係中立地執行工作，咁點解淨係執行政府嘅意願，唔執行埋人民嘅意願？<br />\n<br />\n明明就係收咗錢就對上級無條件服從，甚至算係被收買咗受政府指使執行政治任務。警察或機械人盲目執行幕後政治推手嘅非中立指令，係咪都算係政治中立？<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記啲錢來自人民中嘅納稅人，政府本來應該代表大部分人民嘅意願，所以公務員嘅政治取態應該等於多數人民嘅取態，服從人民嘅意願。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上是否合理？</strong>"},{"pid":"60b9971778c197565b20224d1ca014de00466832","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"以上是否合理？？"},{"pid":"71887fd245389dd0467341bc059ab1e04d7bed21","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"講得唔啱咩？"},{"pid":"411b5f02473fadeeebb509da76c0d40c62a02d4a","tid":1393224,"uid":62154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RC16Or3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRC16Or3.png&h=1bf45647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1QO1MM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1QO1MM.jpg&h=035465cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipct1MM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fipct1MM.jpg&h=c682fdd6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gM6RZys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgM6RZys.jpg&h=4d206299&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaYEoZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaYEoZ7.jpg&h=219e89ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c102aaefd4c640aec541334b13eb7a1fac62de0e","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"政治中立 <strong>不等於</strong> 服從政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政治中立 <strong>等於</strong> 服從政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f09b09099ae28e5f336b6600f4f428dffae09f","tid":1393224,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"pls study more<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/1672.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2F1672.html&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=908cae0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/1672.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkccsa.org/old/old_content/WYP/200/P14_17.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkccsa.org%2Fold%2Fold_content%2FWYP%2F200%2FP14_17.pdf&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=1ea91963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkccsa.org/old/old_content/WYP/200/P14_17.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://p-articles.com/critics/933.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp-articles.com%2Fcritics%2F933.html&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=8b8acfdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p-articles.com/critics/933.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/content/%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fcontent%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E3%2580%2581%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=1e8e2a78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/content/%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93</a>"},{"pid":"8e04563a5aa1b2eb63a613d4c9f12700bb4cdc2b","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"thx<br />\n&quot;（ 一 ）   公 務 員 的 政 治 中 立 ， 建 基 於 效 忠 政 府...&quot;<br />\n但政府就政治中立？<br />\n&quot;（ 五 ）   在 執 行 公 務 時 不 偏 不 倚 &quot;<br />\n政府非政治中立，效忠政府如何不偏不倚？<br />\n<br />\n如果公務員冇獨立思考何謂中立，就只係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收咗錢受政府指使</span>..."},{"pid":"7285bb7af7defd037831dcae2846868147b84af2","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"如果政治中立，就應該忠實履行〝一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治〞同基本法憲制責任。"},{"pid":"0ca75f17fa78584aaf448a0c37798290b68a9f08","tid":1393224,"uid":108337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果真係政治中立，就唔應該主動話人政治唔中立<br />\n因為你話人政治唔中立果刻已經係政治唔中立</span>"},{"pid":"15cc8b2680d6db70820f78274a34209b881e0305","tid":1393224,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"026e92ad59a34a8e4ca6c5da241c6027c4971646","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"政府有政治取態（支持修例、不作調查等），<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>支持政府就係支持一種政治取態</ins></span>，點算係政治中立？公務員根本唔係政治中立，中立唔係要不偏幫嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果係中立地執行工作，咁點解淨係執行政府嘅意願，唔執行埋人民嘅意願？<br />\n<br />\n明明就係收咗錢就對上級無條件服從，甚至算係被收買咗受政府指使執行政治任務。警察或機械人盲目執行幕後政治推手嘅非中立指令，係咪都算係政治中立？<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記啲錢來自人民中嘅納稅人，政府本來應該代表大部分人民嘅意願，所以公務員嘅政治取態應該等於多數人民嘅取態，服從人民嘅意願。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上是否合理？</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"人民意願有咁多唔同種類 點樣執行？"},{"pid":"7bc79aedbe86975bdea4a66052904c59f7c8744d","tid":1393224,"uid":274435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"政治中立係執行職務上不分立場<br />\n不過去到有返咁上下大粒本身係就係代表政府立場"},{"pid":"b95c8a9b1b2cd6dc978aaff085207384717713a3","tid":1393224,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"Nothing can override humanity including law and order.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bb57cb41fc3c4378f70bf00e44b6da5ef4c4e5","tid":1393224,"uid":47153,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"政治中立唔係咁解, 讀多啲書先啦小朋友"},{"pid":"0a24b1f352403db2020b21a9e8bdfa1a6dd2ca2e","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15cc8b2680d6db70820f78274a34209b881e0305","tid":1393224,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"026e92ad59a34a8e4ca6c5da241c6027c4971646","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"政府有政治取態（支持修例、不作調查等），<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>支持政府就係支持一種政治取態</ins></span>，點算係政治中立？公務員根本唔係政治中立，中立唔係要不偏幫嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果係中立地執行工作，咁點解淨係執行政府嘅意願，唔執行埋人民嘅意願？<br />\n<br />\n明明就係收咗錢就對上級無條件服從，甚至算係被收買咗受政府指使執行政治任務。警察或機械人盲目執行幕後政治推手嘅非中立指令，係咪都算係政治中立？<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記啲錢來自人民中嘅納稅人，政府本來應該代表大部分人民嘅意願，所以公務員嘅政治取態應該等於多數人民嘅取態，服從人民嘅意願。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上是否合理？</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"人民意願有咁多唔同種類 點樣執行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"如果有重要嘢 只可揀A或B，最好有快速電子公投，少數服從多數 ~"},{"pid":"fe8c225c3f357cab984236c37e6f5d10b55b18b1","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85bb57cb41fc3c4378f70bf00e44b6da5ef4c4e5","tid":1393224,"uid":47153,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"政治中立唔係咁解, 讀多啲書先啦小朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"政府嘅解釋包括 效忠、服從、支持政府（唔係人民），咪同堅決服從擁護黨差唔多？<br />\n<br />\n而家就係講緊 政治中立應該點樣解，唔係政府點樣解。<br />\n<br />\n而且公務員理應服務納稅人/人民，唔係納稅人養嘅政府，除非政府就係代表緊多數人民嘅政治立場。"},{"pid":"eeea49e1046f436c2d3b3fcc9a918476a5d22a54","tid":1393224,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"依家喺香港反政府 = 犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n_______________________<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"5c514a8ad099ba7cdf1390ed8441e8aabd30f10f","tid":1393224,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"85127dad4bd6b34a45b9dc4af339f9a6aed9acfd","tid":1393224,"uid":51931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"中立只係扮民主社會好聽啲既講法 <br />\n說穿了港共要求既係深藍立場"},{"pid":"68cd9161e5b692ba752bb327aea37e3f15eddc3b","tid":1393224,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeea49e1046f436c2d3b3fcc9a918476a5d22a54","tid":1393224,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"依家喺香港反政府 = 犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n_______________________<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"如果係政治中立，無論反政府定撐政府都應該聽，唔可以唔聽泛民意見。"},{"pid":"f08c7b0f5146e55